properties.name: LuxAir
properties.descript: Luxair, legally Luxair S.A., Société Luxembourgeoise de Navigation Aérienne, is the flag carrier of Luxembourg with its headquarters and hub at Luxembourg Airport.

properties.name: SwissAir
properties.descript: Swiss International Air Lines AG, colloquially known as SWISS, is the flag carrier of Switzerland and a subsidiary of the Lufthansa Group, as well as a Star Alliance member.

properties.name: KLM
properties.descript: KLM Royal Dutch Airlines, legally Koninklijke Luchtvaart Maatschappij N.V., is the flag carrier of the Netherlands. KLM is headquartered in Amstelveen, with its hub at nearby Amsterdam Airport Schiphol.

properties.name: British Airways
properties.descript: British Airways is the flag carrier airline of the United Kingdom. It is headquartered in London, England, near its main hub at Heathrow Airport. The airline is the second largest UK-based carrier.

properties.name: ITA Airways
properties.descript: Italia Trasporto Aereo S.p.A., trading as ITA Airways, is the flag carrier of Italy, and the largest Italian airline by total number of passengers carried, by number of destinations served, and by fleet size.

properties.name: CityJet
properties.descript: CityJet is an Irish regional airline with headquarters at Dublin Airport.
